tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fitness_tracker (
  user_id INT,
  activity_date DATE,
  fitness_activity TEXT,
  duration_minutes INT
)

CREATE TABLE fitness_routines (
    id UUID NOT NULL,
    routine_name STRING NOT NULL,
    duration INT NOT NULL,
    calories_burned INT NOT NULL,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
);

CREATE TABLE health_goals (
    id UUID NOT NULL,
    goal_description STRING NOT NULL,
    current_status STRING NOT NULL,
    target_date DATE NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
);

CREATE TABLE fitness_routines (
    routine_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    routine_name TEXT,
    intensity_level TEXT,
    duration_minutes INT
);

CREATE TABLE health_goals (
    goal_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    goal_description TEXT,
    target_weight DECIMAL,
    target_calories INT
);

CREATE TABLE meditation_practices (
    practice_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    practice_date DATE,
    duration_minutes INT,
    meditation_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE travelers (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT,
    country_of_origin TEXT,
    current_location TEXT,
    current_city TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE locations_visited (
    visit_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    location_name TEXT,
    visit_date DATE,
    duration_days INT
);
